#: ../../source/user_guide/dsp_effects.rst:2
#: 874dd54387384dcab85d7f37bf97821c
msgid "DSP 效果器"
msgstr "DSP Effects"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dsp_effects.rst:4
#: 7821d15513a841abacf18284b76c5bf0
msgid "本章讲“怎样给声音加效果”。"
msgstr "This chapter explains how to add effects to sounds."

#: ../../source/user_guide/dsp_effects.rst:6
#: a89df723353d45049478deb07e1f5ac7
msgid ""
":ref:`DSP<glossary-dsp>` 是音频效果处理单元。混响、滤波、延迟、压缩、频谱分析都可以看成 DSP。刚开始使用时，建议优先用 ``FmodAudioEffect*`` 这些资源类，把效果加到 :ref:`Bus<glossary-bus>` 上；只有需要非常底层的控制时，再直接操作 :ref:`FmodDSP<FmodDSP>`。"
msgstr ""
"A :ref:`DSP<glossary-dsp>` is an audio effect processing unit. Reverb, filtering, delay, compression, and spectrum analysis can all be treated as DSPs. When getting started, prefer the ``FmodAudioEffect*`` resource classes and add effects to a :ref:`Bus<glossary-bus>`. Use :ref:`FmodDSP<FmodDSP>` directly only when you need very low-level control."

